ent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-119 ng-star-inserted" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="model-thoughts ng-tns-c1786796508-119"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header ng-tns-c1786796508-119"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" mat-button="" data-test-id="thoughts-header-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c1786796508-119 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c1786796508-119"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-119">Mostrar raciocínio</span></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c1786796508-119"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c1786796508-119 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button></div><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----><!----><!----><!----><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="model-response-text ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3841436833="" id="message-content-id-r_994d8f7a4a059ff3" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3841436833="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_994d8f7a4a059ff3" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:120">Claro, aqui está uma sugestão de mensagem de commit que resume as alterações realizadas, no formato convencional do Git:</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-121 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-121 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_994d8f7a4a059ff3&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_3e375bee6b864ba6&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-121"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-121"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-121"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-121 no-decoration-radius" data-sourcepos="3:1-14:249">feat(assets): Adiciona fundos de mapa dinâmicos por fase

O commit implementa a lógica necessária para carregar e exibir imagens de fundo (backgrounds) específicas para cada fase do jogo.

Anteriormente, os assets de imagem para os fundos de mapa (`forest.png`, `vulcan.png`, etc.) eram declarados em `config.js` e carregados no início do jogo, mas nunca eram renderizados no canvas. A função de desenho procurava uma propriedade `bg` na configuração da fase atual, que não estava sendo definida.

As seguintes alterações foram realizadas para corrigir o problema:

- **`config.js`**: Foi criada a função `linkPhaseBackgrounds` para associar as imagens de fundo já carregadas às suas respectivas configurações no array `phaseConfigs`.
- **`main.js`**: A nova função `linkPhaseBackgrounds` é chamada dentro da função `loadAssets`. Isso garante que a associação ocorra somente após a conclusão do carregamento de todas as imagens, disponibilizando a imagem correta para a função `draw`.
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element></div></message-content><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-footer gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c3831108472="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c3831108472="" _nghost-ng-c1702140789="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c3572881400="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3358885363-117"><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c1790889713="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-122 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-122"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-122 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" _nghost-ng-c1126443278="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-122 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1126443278="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Boa resposta" aria-label="Boa resposta" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger icon-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-butt