<li data-sourcepos="41:3-45:0"><strong>O que mudou?</strong>
<ul data-sourcepos="42:7-45:0">
<li data-sourcepos="42:7-42:87">Removemos a linha <code>&lt;p&gt;Vida: &lt;span id="health-text"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</code>.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="43:7-43:119">Movemos o container da barra de vida (<code>player-health-container</code>) para dentro da <code>div</code> com a classe <code>hud-stats</code>.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="44:7-45:0">Adicionamos um <code>span</code> com o id <code>player-health-text</code> dentro do container da barra. Ele servirá para mostrar o valor numérico da vida sobre a barra.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul><h3 data-sourcepos="46:1-46:35">Passo 2: Adicionar o Estilo CSS</h3><p data-sourcepos="48:1-48:144">Agora, vamos estilizar a barra de vida. Usaremos um estilo parecido com o que você já tem para a barra do chefe, garantindo consistência visual.</p><p data-sourcepos="50:1-50:82"><strong>Adicione o seguinte código ao seu arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/css/healthBar.css</code>:</strong></p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-134 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-134 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_e6b6dbb241bbe1ec&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_b12f379db0bb64c3&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-134 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-134">CSS</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-134 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-134 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_e6b6dbb241bbe1ec&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_b12f379db0bb64c3&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-134"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-134"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-134"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-134" data-sourcepos="52:1-81:1"><span class="hljs-comment">/* Barra de vida do Jogador */</span>
<span class="hljs-selector-id">#player-health-container</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: relative; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Necessário para posicionar o texto sobre a barra */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">width</span>: <span class="hljs-number">180px</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">height</span>: <span class="hljs-number">22px</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-color</span>: <span class="hljs-number">#555</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">border</span>: <span class="hljs-number">2px</span> solid <span class="hljs-number">#222</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">border-radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">5px</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">display</span>: flex;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">align-items</span>: center;
}

<span class="hljs-selector-id">#player-health-bar</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">height</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100%</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-color</span>: <span class="hljs-number">#28a745</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Verde para vida cheia */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">border-radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">3px</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">transition</span>: width <span class="hljs-number">0.3s</span> ease-in-out; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Animação suave */</span>
}

<span class="hljs-selector-id">#player-health-text</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: absolute;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">width</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100%</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">text-align</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">color</span>: white;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="hljs-number">14px</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">font-weight</span>: bold;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">text-shadow</span>: <span class="hljs-number">1px</span> <span class="hljs-number">1px</span> <span class="hljs-number">1px</span> black; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Sombra para melhor legibilidade */</span>
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><h3 data-sourcepos="83:1-83:42">Passo 3: Atualizar a Lógica em <code>ui.js</code></h3><p data-sourcepos="85:1-85:136">Finalmente, vamos ajustar a função <code>drawHUD</code> para que ela atualize corretamente a largura da barra de vida e o texto que fica sobre ela.</p><p data-sourcepos="87:1-87:72"><strong>No arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/js/ui.js</code>, modifique a função <code>drawHUD</code>:</strong></p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-135 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-135 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_e6b6dbb241bbe1ec&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_b12f379db0bb64c3&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-135 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-135">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-135 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-135 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_e6b6dbb241bbe1ec&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_b12f379db0bb64c3&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-135"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-135"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-135"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-135" data-sourcepos="89:1-116:1"><span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">drawHUD</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>) </span>{
  <span class="hljs-comment">// Sai da função se o jogador ainda não existe</span>
  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!gameState.player) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;

  <span class="hljs-comment">// --- Lógica da Barra de Vida do Jogador ---</span>
  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> playerHealthPercent = (gameState.player.health / gameState.player.maxHealth) * <span class="hljs-number">100</span>;
  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> playerHealthBar = <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="hljs-string">"player-health-bar"</span>);
  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (playerHealthBar) {
    playerHealthBar.style.width = <span class="hljs-string">`<span class="hljs-subst">${playerHealthPercent}</span>%`</span>;
  }
  
  <span class="hljs-comment">// Atualiza o texto da vida sobre a barra</span>
  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> healthText = <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="hljs-string">"player-health-text"</span>); <span class="hljs-comment">// &lt;&lt;&lt; Mude o ID aqui</span>
  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (healthText) {
    healthText.textContent = gameState.player.health;
  }

  <span class="hljs-comment">// Atualiza outros textos da HUD</span>
  <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="hljs-string">"phase-text"</span>).textContent = gameState.phase + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;
  <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="hljs-string">"score-text"</span>).textContent = gameState.score;
  
  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> config = phaseConfigs[gameState.phase];
  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!config) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;

  <span class="hljs-comment">// ... (o resto da função permanece igual)</span>
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><ul data-sourcepos="118:3-120:0">
<li data-sourcepos="118:3-120:0"><strong>O que mudou?</strong>
<ul data-sourcepos="119:7-120:0">
<li data-sourcepos="119:7-120:0">A única mudança real foi na linha <code>const healthText = document.getElementById("player-health-text");</code>. Alteramos o seletor para pegar o novo <code>span</code> que está sobre a barra, garantindo que o valor da vida continue sendo exibido.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul><p data-sourcepos="121:1-121:157">Com essas três alterações, seu jogo agora terá uma barra de vida funcional e visualmente agradável para o personagem, que diminui suavemente ao receber dano.</p></div></message-content><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-footer gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c3831108472="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c3831108472="" _nghost-ng-c1702140789="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c3572881400="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3358885363-125"><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c1790889713="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-136 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-136"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-136 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" _nghost-ng-c1126443278="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-136 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1126443278="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Boa resposta" aria-label="Boa resposta" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger icon-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-pressed="false" aria-controls="feedback-form-2" jslog="173913;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey: