oader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c1786796508-141"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-141">Mostrar raciocínio</span></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c1786796508-141"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c1786796508-141 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button></div><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----><!----><!----><!----><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="model-response-text ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3841436833="" id="message-content-id-r_ac468f802f9acd81" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3841436833="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_ac468f802f9acd81" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:146">Olá! Isso é um ajuste comum e bem simples de fazer. O tamanho do seu projétil está definido por uma variável dentro da função de tiro do jogador.</p><p data-sourcepos="3:1-3:81">Para aumentar o tamanho do sprite do seu projétil, você precisa fazer o seguinte:</p><h3 data-sourcepos="5:1-5:51">Passo 1: Localize o Arquivo e a Função Corretos</h3><p data-sourcepos="7:1-7:86">O código que controla a criação de projéteis está no arquivo de entidades do seu jogo.</p><ol data-sourcepos="9:1-12:0">
<li data-sourcepos="9:1-9:52">Abra o arquivo: <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/js/entities.js</code></li>
<li data-sourcepos="10:1-10:53">Dentro desse arquivo, encontre a classe <code>Player</code>.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="11:1-12:0">Procure pelo método chamado <code>shoot(direction)</code> dentro da classe <code>Player</code>.</li>
</ol><h3 data-sourcepos="13:1-13:41">Passo 2: Altere a Variável de Tamanho</h3><p data-sourcepos="15:1-15:169">Dentro do método <code>shoot</code>, você encontrará uma constante chamada <code>projSize</code> que define o tamanho (largura e altura) do projétil. Atualmente, ela está com o valor de <code>10</code>.</p><p data-sourcepos="17:1-17:80"><strong>No arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/js/entities.js</code>, encontre este trecho de código:</strong></p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-144 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-144 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_ac468f802f9acd81&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c933b310b736a134&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-144 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-144">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-144 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-144 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_ac468f802f9acd81&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c933b310b736a134&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripp