</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><ul data-sourcepos="51:3-52:0">
<li data-sourcepos="51:3-52:0"><strong>Por que essa mudança?</strong> Isso simplifica o layout. Agora, <code>.hud-top</code> organiza três itens em linha: a barra de vida, as estatísticas de fase/pontos e o botão de pausa. Isso evita que os estilos de <code>hud-stats</code> afetem a barra de vida.</li>
</ul><h4 data-sourcepos="53:1-53:53">Passo 2: Garantir que o CSS está sendo Carregado</h4><p data-sourcepos="55:1-55:166">O <code>index.html</code> principal está linkando apenas o <code>main.css</code>. Todos os outros arquivos CSS (<code>healthBar.css</code>, <code>hud.css</code>, etc.) não estão sendo carregados pelo navegador.</p><p data-sourcepos="57:1-57:79">A solução mais simples é consolidar todos os estilos necessários em <code>main.css</code>.</p><p data-sourcepos="59:1-59:137"><strong>Copie todo o conteúdo do seu arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/css/healthBar.css</code> e cole-o no final do arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/css/main.css</code>.</strong></p><p data-sourcepos="61:1-61:51">O conteúdo a ser copiado de <code>healthBar.css</code> é este:</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-157 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-157 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_90bc60cdc8bc9b2d&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_a5fe3e6cc8dd3e00&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-157 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-157">CSS</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-157 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-157 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_90bc60cdc8bc9b2d&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_a5fe3e6cc8dd3e00&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-157"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-157"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-157"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-157" data-sourcepos="63:1-92:1"><span class="hljs-comment">/* Barra de vida do Jogador */</span>
<span class="hljs-selector-id">#player-health-container</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: relative;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">width</span>: <span class="hljs-number">180px</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">height</span>: <span class="hljs-number">22px</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-color</span>: <span class="hljs-number">#555</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">border</span>: <span class="hljs-number">2px</span> solid <span class="hljs-number">#222</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">border-radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">5px</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">display</span>: flex;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">align-items</span>: center;
}

<span class="hljs-selector-id">#player-health-bar</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">height</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100%</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-color</span>: <span class="hljs-number">#28a745</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">border-radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">3px</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">transition</span>: width <span class="hljs-number">0.3s</span> ease-in-out;
}

<span class="hljs-selector-id">#player-health-text</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: absolute;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">width</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100%</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">text-align</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">color</span>: white;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="hljs-number">14px</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">font-weight</span>: bold;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">text-shadow</span>: <span class="hljs-number">1px</span> <span class="hljs-number">1px</span> <span class="hljs-number">1px</span> black;
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><p data-sourcepos="94:1-94:230">Ao fazer essas duas correções (ajustar o HTML e consolidar o CSS), a barra de vida deverá aparecer corretamente no seu HUD, pois a estrutura HTML estará mais limpa e o navegador terá acesso aos estilos necessários para desenhá-la.</p></div></message-content><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-footer gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c3831108472="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c3831108472="" _nghost-ng-c1702140789="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c3572881400="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3358885363-149"><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c1790889713="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-158 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-158"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-158 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" _nghost-ng-c1126443278="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-158 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c112644327