#__lottie_element_2978)"><g transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,16,16)" opacity="1" style="display: block;"><g opacity="1" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_3005)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="2" d=" M-4.383999824523926,-14.347999572753906 C-2.996999979019165,-14.772000312805176 -1.524999976158142,-15 0,-15 C0,-15 0,-15 0,-15 C1.7100000381469727,-15 3.3540000915527344,-14.713000297546387 4.886000156402588,-14.1850004196167"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,16,16)" opacity="1"><g opacity="1" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_3001)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="2" d=" M-4.564000129699707,-14.291999816894531 C-3.125,-14.751999855041504 -1.590999960899353,-15 0,-15 C0,-15 0,-15 0,-15 C1.6440000534057617,-15 3.2269999980926514,-14.734999656677246 4.706999778747559,-14.244999885559082"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,16,16)" opacity="1"><g opacity="1" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_2997)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="2" d=" M-10.402999877929688,-10.802000045776367 C-7.704999923706055,-13.401000022888184 -4.038000106811523,-15 0,-15 C0,-15 0,-15 0,-15 C0,-15 0,-15 0,-15"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_2993)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_2989)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_2982)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div><!----><!----></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c3358885363-217 has-thoughts"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-content ng-tns-c3358885363-217"><!----><model-thoughts _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-220 ng-star-inserted" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="model-thoughts ng-tns-c1786796508-220"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header ng-tns-c1786796508-220"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" mat-button="" data-test-id="thoughts-header-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c1786796508-220 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c1786796508-220"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-220">Mostrar raciocínio</span></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c1786796508-220"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c1786796508-220 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button></div><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----><!----><!----><!----><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="model-response-text ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3841436833="" id="message-content-id-r_1200ebe08aa96b3b" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3841436833="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_1200ebe08aa96b3b" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:169">Olá! Bem observado. Essa barra cinza apareceu por uma pequena inconsistência de tamanho entre o contêiner principal do jogo e o conteúdo dentro dele (o HUD e o canvas).</p><h3 data-sourcepos="3:1-3:23">A Causa do Problema</h3><ol data-sourcepos="5:1-10:0">
<li data-sourcepos="5:1-5:96">No arquivo <code>main.css</code>, a "caixa" do jogo (<code>#game-wrapper</code>) tem uma altura fixa de <strong>600px</strong>.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="6:1-6:101">O seu HUD (a parte de cima com a vida, fase, etc.) ocupa uma certa altura (aproximadamente 68px).</li>
<li data-sourcepos="7:1-7:104">No arquivo <code>config.js</code>, a altura do canvas do jogo (<code>VIEWPORT_HEIGHT</code>) está definida como <strong>520px</strong>.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="8:1-8:70">Somando a altura do HUD e do canvas, temos <code>68px + 520px = 588px</code>.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="9:1-10:0">A barra cinza que você vê é a diferença: <code>600px (caixa total) - 588px (conteúdo) = 12px</code> de espaço vazio no fundo, que mostra a cor de fundo cinza (<code>#222</code>) do <code>#game-wrapper</code>.</li>
</ol><h3 data-sourcepos="11:1-11:13">A Solução</h3><p data-sourcepos="13:1-13:155">A solução mais simples e correta é fazer o canvas do jogo ocupar exatamente esse espaço que sobrou. Para isso, basta ajustar a constante <code>VIEWPORT_HEIGHT</code>.</p><p data-sourcepos="15:1-15:53"><strong>1. Abra o arquivo:</strong> <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/js/config.js</code></p><p data-sourcepos="17:1-17:39"><strong>2. Encontre estas linhas de código:</strong></p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-224 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-224 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_1200ebe08aa96b3b&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_2929559590c02c51&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-224 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-224">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-224 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-224 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_1200ebe08aa96b3b&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_2929559590c02c51&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-224"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-224"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-224"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-224" data-sourcepos="19:1-24:58"><span class="hljs-comment">// MODIFICADO: Define o tamanho da área de jogo para 600px de largura.</span>
<span class="hljs-comment">// A altura é um pouco menor para dar espaço ao HUD dentro da caixa.</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> VIEWPORT_WIDTH = <span class="hljs-number">600</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> VIEWPORT_HEIGHT = <span class="hljs-number">520</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// &lt;---- ESTA LINHA</span>
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><p data-sourcepos="26:1-26:63"><strong>3. Altere o valor de <code>VIEWPORT_HEIGHT</code> de <code>520</code> para <code>532</code>:</strong></p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-225 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-225 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_1200ebe08aa96b3b&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_2929559590c02c51&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-225 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-225">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-225 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-225 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_1200ebe08aa96b3b&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_2929559590c02c51&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-225"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-225"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-225"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-225" data-sourcepos="28:1-33:62"><span class="hljs-comment">// MODIFICADO: Define o tamanho da área de jogo para 600px de largura.</span>
<span class="hljs-comment">// A altura é um pouco menor para dar espaço ao HUD dentro da caixa.</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> VIEWPORT_WIDTH = <span class="hljs-number">600</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> VIEWPORT_HEIGHT = <span class="hljs-number">532</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// &lt;---- VALOR AJUSTADO</span>
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><p data-sourcepos="35:1-35:171">Ao fazer essa pequena alteração, o canvas do seu jogo passará a ter a altura exata para preencher o espaço restante dentro da caixa de 600px, e a barra cinza desaparecerá.</p></div></message-content><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-footer gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c3831108472="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c3831108472="" _nghost-ng-c1702140789="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c3572881400="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3358885363-217"><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c1790889713="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-226 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-226"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-226 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" _nghost-ng-c1126443278="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-226 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1126443278="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Boa resposta" aria-labe