n _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c1786796508-239 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more" style=""></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button></div><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----><!----><!----><!----><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="model-response-text ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3841436833="" id="message-content-id-r_002b3b402f92357d" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3841436833="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_002b3b402f92357d" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:89">Entendido. A imagem anterior talvez não tenha capturado o estilo "pixel art" do seu jogo.</p><p data-sourcepos="3:1-3:113">Vamos tentar uma abordagem diferente, focando em uma estética que combine melhor com os gráficos que você já tem.</p><p data-sourcepos="5:1-5:19">Que tal esta ideia?</p><p data-sourcepos="7:1-7:421">Uma cena em pixel art mostrando a entrada de uma masmorra à noite. Um arco de pedra, coberto de musgo e vinhas, está embutido na encosta de uma montanha rochosa. A entrada escura é ladeada por duas tochas, cujo fogo pixelado lança um brilho laranja e tremeluzente. Um caminho de paralelepípedos leva à entrada. Ao fundo, uma floresta escura se recorta contra um céu estrelado. O estilo é de um videogame retrô de 16-bits.</p><p data-sourcepos="9:1-9:37">Vou gerar essa nova imagem para você.</p><p data-sourcepos="11:1-11:55">http://googleusercontent.com/image_generation_content/1</p></div></message-content><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-footer gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted" style=""><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c3831108472="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c3831108472="" _nghost-ng-c1702140789="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c3572881400="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3358885363-237"><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c1790889713="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-240 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-240"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-240 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" _nghost-ng-c1126443278="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-240 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1126443278="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Boa resposta" aria-label="Boa resposta" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger icon-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-pressed="false" aria-controls="feedback-form-12" jslog="173913;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_002b3b402f92357d&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_af09c2ab41a5d9c4&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c