6 -1.524999976158142,-15 0,-15 C0,-15 0,-15 0,-15 C1.7100000381469727,-15 3.3540000915527344,-14.713000297546387 4.886000156402588,-14.1850004196167"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_3505)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_3501)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_3494)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div><!----><!----></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c3358885363-249 has-thoughts"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-content ng-tns-c3358885363-249"><!----><model-thoughts _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-251 ng-star-inserted" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="model-thoughts ng-tns-c1786796508-251"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header ng-tns-c1786796508-251"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" mat-button="" data-test-id="thoughts-header-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c1786796508-251 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c1786796508-251"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-251">Mostrar raciocínio</span></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c1786796508-251"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c1786796508-251 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button></div><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----><!----><!----><!----><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="model-response-text ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3841436833="" id="message-content-id-r_94437d4a21e2a307" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3841436833="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_94437d4a21e2a307" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:157">Ótima pergunta! O processo é bem simples e envolve duas etapas: salvar a imagem na pasta correta e depois aplicar essa imagem como fundo do menu usando CSS.</p><h3 data-sourcepos="3:1-3:28">Passo 1: Salvar a Imagem</h3><ol data-sourcepos="5:1-8:0">
<li data-sourcepos="5:1-5:149">Primeiro, você precisa salvar a imagem que eu gerei. Clique com o botão direito na imagem da minha resposta anterior e salve-a no seu computador.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="6:1-6:76">Renomeie o arquivo para <code>menu-background.png</code> (ou um nome que preferir).</li>
<li data-sourcepos="7:1-8:0">Mova este arquivo de imagem para a pasta <code>images</code> que está dentro do seu projeto (<code>ECOM00_jogo/images/</code>). Esta é a mesma pasta onde estão seus outros sprites, como <code>pistol.png</code> e <code>forest.png</code>.</li>
</ol><h3 data-sourcepos="9:1-9:33">Passo 2: Editar o CSS do Menu</h3><p data-sourcepos="11:1-11:119">Agora, vamos dizer ao jogo para usar essa imagem como fundo do menu inicial. Faremos isso no seu arquivo CSS principal.</p><ol data-sourcepos="13:1-37:0">
<li data-sourcepos="13:1-14:0">
<p data-sourcepos="13:5-13:54"><strong>Abra o arquivo:</strong> <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/css/main.css</code></p>
</li>
<li data-sourcepos="15:1-35:0">
<p data-sourcepos="15:5-15:84"><strong>Encontre a regra de estilo para <code>#start-menu</code></strong>. Ela deve se parecer com isto:</p>
<response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-254 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-254 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_94437d4a21e2a307&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_584167d4b8672d35&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-254 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-254">CSS</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-254 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-254 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_94437d4a21e2a307&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_584167d4b8672d35&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-254"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-254"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-254"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-254" data-sourcepos="17:5-34:5"><span class="hljs-selector-id">#start-menu</span>, <span class="hljs-selector-id">#pause-menu</span>, <span class="hljs-selector-id">#message-screen</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: absolute;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">top</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">left</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">width</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100%</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">height</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100%</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-color</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">10</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.95</span>);
  <span class="hljs-attribute">display</span>: flex;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">flex-direction</span>: column;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">justify-content</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">align-items</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">text-align</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">font-family</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"Press Start 2P"</span>, cursive;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">z-index</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">color</span>: <span class="hljs-number">#fff</span>;
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>
</li>
<li data-sourcepos="36:1-37:0">
<p data-sourcepos="36:5-36:171"><strong>Substitua essa regra inteira</strong> pela versão abaixo. A nova versão remove o seletor <code>#start-menu</code> da regra geral e cria uma regra específica para ele com o fundo novo.</p>
</li>
</ol><p data-sourcepos="38:1-38:20">&lt;!-- end list --&gt;</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-255 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-255 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_94437d4a21e2a307&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_584167d4b8672d35&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-255 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-255">CSS</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-255 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-255 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_94437d4a21e2a307&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_584167d4b8672d35&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-255"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-255"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-255"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-255" data-sourcepos="40:1-89:1"><span class="hljs-comment">/* Em main.css */</span>

<span class="hljs-comment">/* Regra específica para o menu inicial com a imagem de fundo */</span>
<span class="hljs-selector-id">#start-menu</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: absolute; <span class="hljs-comment">/* ou 'fixed' se estiver fora do wrapper */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">top</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">left</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">width</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100%</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">height</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100%</span>;
  
  <span class="hljs-comment">/* --- A MÁGICA ACONTECE AQUI --- */</span>
  <span class="hljs-comment">/* Define a imagem de fundo. O caminho é relativo ao arquivo CSS. */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-image</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">linear-gradient</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.6</span>), <span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.6</span>)), <span class="hljs-built_in">url</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'../../images/menu-background.png'</span>);
  
  <span class="hljs-comment">/* Faz a imagem cobrir toda a tela sem distorcer */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-size</span>: cover;
  
  <span class="hljs-comment">/* Centraliza a imagem */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-position</span>: center;

  <span class="hljs-attribute">display</span>: flex;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">flex-direction</span>: column;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">justify-content</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">align-items</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">text-align</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">font-family</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"Press Start 2P"</span>, cursive;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">z-index</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">color</span>: <span class="hljs-number">#fff</span>;
}


<span class="hljs-comment">/* Regra para os outros menus, que continuam com o fundo preto */</span>
<span class="hljs-selector-id">#pause-menu</span>, <span class="hljs-selector-id">#message-screen</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: absolute;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">top</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">left</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">width</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100%</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">height</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100%</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-color</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">10</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.95</span>);
  <span class="hljs-attribute">display</span>: flex;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">flex-direction</span>: column;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">justify-content</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">align-items</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">text-align</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">font-family</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"Press Start 2P"</span>, cursive;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">z-index</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">color</span>: <span class="hljs-number">#fff</span>;
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><ul data-sourcepos="91:3-97:0">
<li data-sourcepos="91:3-97:0"><strong>O que mudou?</strong>
<ul data-sourcepos="92:7-97:0">
<li data-sourcepos="92:7-92:89">Separamos a regra do <code>#start-menu</code> das outras (<code>#pause-menu</code>, <code>#message-screen</code>).</li>
<li data-sourcepos="93:7-93:100"><strong><code>background-image</code></strong>: Esta é a linha mais importante. Ela aplica a imagem que você salvou.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="94:7-94:219"><strong><code>linear-gradient(...)</code></strong>: Adicionei um filtro preto semitransparente sobre a imagem. Isso é um truque para escurecer um pouco o fundo e garantir que o texto branco do título e dos botões continue fácil de ler.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="95:7-95:84"><strong><code>background-size: cover;</code></strong>: Garante que a imagem preencha a tela inteira.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="96:7-97:0"><strong><code>background-position: center;</code></strong>: Centraliza a imagem para um melhor enquadramento.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul><p data-sourcepos="98:1-98:127">Depois de salvar o arquivo <code>main.css</code>, recarregue seu jogo no navegador. O menu inicial agora deve ter a nova imagem de fundo!</p></div></message-content><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-footer gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c3831108472="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c3831108472="" _nghost-ng-c1702140789="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c3572881400="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3358885363-249"><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c1790889713="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-256 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-256"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-256 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" _nghost-ng-c1126443278="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-256 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1126443278="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Boa resposta" aria-label="Boa resposta" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger icon-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-pressed="false" aria-controls="feedback-form-14" jslog="173913;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_94437d4a21e