epos="5:1-5:213">Vou tentar gerar a imagem mais uma vez, do zero, com base na ideia que você havia aprovado: uma cena em <strong>pixel art</strong> da entrada de uma masmorra à noite, com tochas e um ar de mistério, no estilo de um jogo retrô.</p><p data-sourcepos="7:1-7:19">Por favor, aguarde.</p><p data-sourcepos="10:1-10:55">http://googleusercontent.com/image_generation_content/2</p></div></message-content><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-footer gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted" style=""><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c3831108472="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c3831108472="" _nghost-ng-c1702140789="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c3572881400="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3358885363-259"><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c1790889713="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-262 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-262"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-262 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" _nghost-ng-c1126443278="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-262 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1126443278="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Boa resposta" aria-label="Boa resposta" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger icon-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-md