ke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="2" d=" M-4.716000080108643,-14.241999626159668 C-3.2330000400543213,-14.734000205993652 -1.6469999551773071,-15 0,-15 C0,-15 0,-15 0,-15 C1.590999960899353,-15 3.125,-14.751999855041504 4.564000129699707,-14.291999816894531"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,16,16)" opacity="1"><g opacity="1" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_3893)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="2" d=" M-6.50600004196167,-13.517000198364258 C-4.5370001792907715,-14.467000007629395 -2.3299999237060547,-15 0,-15 C0,-15 0,-15 0,-15 C1.0360000133514404,-15 2.046999931335449,-14.895000457763672 3.0239999294281006,-14.694999694824219"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_3889)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_3885)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_3878)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div><!----><!----></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c3358885363-271 has-thoughts"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-content ng-tns-c3358885363-271"><!----><model-thoughts _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-274 ng-star-inserted" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="model-thoughts ng-tns-c1786796508-274"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header ng-tns-c1786796508-274"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" mat-button="" data-test-id="thoughts-header-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c1786796508-274 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c1786796508-274"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-274">Mostrar raciocínio</span></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c1786796508-274"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c1786796508-274 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button></div><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----><!----><!----><!----><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="model-response-text ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3841436833="" id="message-content-id-r_c3b1248a95ff8ddc" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3841436833="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_c3b1248a95ff8ddc" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:168">A imagem que você postou com o erro 404 da Google confirma o que eu temia: o link que a minha ferramenta de geração de imagens criou é inválido ou expira rápido demais.</p><p data-sourcepos="3:1-3:143">Peço desculpas imensas por todo o transtorno e pela perda de tempo. É uma falha frustrante da minha ferramenta, e você está certo em apontá-la.</p><p data-sourcepos="5:1-5:119">Está claro que não vou conseguir te entregar uma imagem funcional dessa forma. <strong>Por isso, vamos mudar de estratégia.</strong></p><p data-sourcepos="7:1-7:134">Em vez de eu tentar gerar a imagem, vou te ajudar a encontrar uma online e te dar novamente o código exato para colocá-la no seu jogo.</p><h3 data-sourcepos="9:1-9:43">Nova Estratégia: Encontrando uma Imagem</h3><p data-sourcepos="11:1-11:124">Existem ótimos sites onde você pode encontrar imagens de arte para jogos, muitas delas gratuitas para usar em seus projetos.</p><p data-sourcepos="13:1-13:37"><strong>Sugestões de sites para procurar:</strong></p><ol data-sourcepos="15:1-18:0">
<li data-sourcepos="15:1-15:81"><strong>OpenGameArt.org</strong>: Um dos melhores recursos para assets de jogos gratuitos.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="16:1-16:105"><strong>Itch.io (Assets)</strong>: Muitos desenvolvedores disponibilizam pacotes de arte (gratuitos e pagos) aqui.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="17:1-18:0"><strong>Pixabay</strong> ou <strong>Pexels</strong>: Bancos de imagens gerais, mas com filtros de busca que podem te ajudar.</li>
</ol><p data-sourcepos="19:1-19:70"><strong>Termos para pesquisar (em inglês geralmente traz mais resultados):</strong></p><ul data-sourcepos="21:3-25:0">
<li data-sourcepos="21:3-21:34"><code>pixel art dungeon background</code></li>
<li data-sourcepos="22:3-22:26"><code>16-bit cave entrance</code></li>
<li data-sourcepos="23:3-23:28"><code>pixel art forest night</code></li>
<li data-sourcepos="24:3-25:0"><code>free game background</code></li>
</ul><h3 data-sourcepos="26:1-26:43">Como Colocar a Imagem que Você Escolher</h3><p data-sourcepos="28:1-28:133">Assim que você encontrar e baixar uma imagem que te agrade, o processo para colocar no jogo é exatamente o que eu havia te explicado.</p><p data-sourcepos="30:1-30:27"><strong>Passo 1: Salve a Imagem</strong></p><ul data-sourcepos="32:3-34:0">
<li data-sourcepos="32:3-32:72">Salve a imagem que você escolheu na sua pasta <code>ECOM00_jogo/images/</code>.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="33:3-34:0">Renomeie o arquivo para <code>menu-background.png</code> para facilitar.</li>
</ul><p data-sourcepos="35:1-35:32"><strong>Passo 2: Use este código CSS</strong></p><ul data-sourcepos="37:3-39:0">
<li data-sourcepos="37:3-37:54">Abra o seu arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/css/main.css</code>.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="38:3-39:0">Encontre a regra de estilo para <code>#start-menu</code> (ou adicione se não a encontrar) e cole o código abaixo. Este código vai garantir que a imagem preencha o fundo e que o texto fique legível.</li>
</ul><p data-sourcepos="40:1-40:20">&lt;!-- end list --&gt;</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-276 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-276 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_c3b1248a95ff8ddc&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_16e46e4c0b770666&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-276 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-276">CSS</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-276 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-276 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_c3b1248a95ff8ddc&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_16e46e4c0b770666&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-276"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-276"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-276"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-276" data-sourcepos="42:1-72:1"><span class="hljs-comment">/* Em main.css */</span>

<span class="hljs-comment">/* Regra específica para o menu inicial com a imagem de fundo */</span>
<span class="hljs-selector-id">#start-menu</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: absolute; 
  <span class="hljs-attribute">top</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">left</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">width</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100%</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">height</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100%</span>;
  
  <span class="hljs-comment">/* --- CÓDIGO PARA O FUNDO --- */</span>
  <span class="hljs-comment">/* Ele usa a imagem que você salvou */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-image</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">linear-gradient</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.6</span>), <span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.6</span>)), <span class="hljs-built_in">url</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'../../images/menu-background.png'</span>);
  
  <span class="hljs-comment">/* Faz a imagem cobrir toda a tela sem distorcer */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-size</span>: cover;
  
  <span class="hljs-comment">/* Centraliza a imagem */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-position</span>: center;

  <span class="hljs-attribute">display</span>: flex;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">flex-direction</span>: column;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">justify-content</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">align-items</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">text-align</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">font-family</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"Press Start 2P"</span>, cursive;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">z-index</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">color</span>: <span class="hljs-number">#fff</span>;
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><p data-sourcepos="74:1-74:243">Lamento mais uma vez pela falha da minha ferramenta. Espero que esta nova abordagem te ajude a conseguir o resultado que você quer para o seu menu. Se tiver qualquer dúvida na hora de implementar a imagem que você encontrar, é só me perguntar.</p></div></message-content><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-footer gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c3831108472="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c3831108472="" _nghost-ng-c1702140789="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c3572881400="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3358885363-271"><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c1790889713="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-277 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-277"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-277 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" _nghost-ng-c1126443278="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-277 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-