ass="ng-tns-c1786796508-338 ng-star-inserted" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="model-thoughts ng-tns-c1786796508-338"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header ng-tns-c1786796508-338"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" mat-button="" data-test-id="thoughts-header-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c1786796508-338 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c1786796508-338"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-338">Mostrar raciocínio</span></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c1786796508-338"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c1786796508-338 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button></div><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----><!----><!----><!----><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="model-response-text ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3841436833="" id="message-content-id-r_3c8227074b9dd8a1" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3841436833="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_3c8227074b9dd8a1" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:201">Eu sinceramente peço desculpas. Este é o mesmo erro de antes, acontecendo em um novo arquivo por causa de uma falha nas minhas instruções. É a última vez que isso vai acontecer, vamos consertar de vez.</p><p data-sourcepos="3:1-3:188">O problema em <code>gameLogic.js</code> é que a função <code>showEndScreen</code> está sendo importada duas vezes: uma no topo do arquivo (conforme minhas instruções) e outra que já existia no final do arquivo.</p><h3 data-sourcepos="5:1-5:23">Correção Definitiva</h3><p data-sourcepos="7:1-7:84">Vamos limpar as importações duplicadas no arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/js/gameLogic.js</code>.</p><ol data-sourcepos="9:1-28:0">
<li data-sourcepos="9:1-9:57"><strong>Abra o arquivo:</strong> <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/js/gameLogic.js</code></li>
<li data-sourcepos="10:1-14:7"><strong>Vá até o final do arquivo</strong> e <strong>APAGUE</strong> esta linha, que não deveria estar ali:
<response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-341 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-341 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3c8227074b9dd8a1&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_04ab7d3444922772&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-341 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-341">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-341 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-341 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3c8227074b9dd8a1&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_04ab7d3444922772&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-341"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-341"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-341"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-341" data-sourcepos="11:5-14:44"><span class="hljs-comment">// Apague esta linha do final do arquivo</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> { showEndScreen } <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <span class="hljs-string">'./ui.js'</span>;
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>
</li>
<li data-sourcepos="15:1-28:0"><strong>Agora, vá para o topo do arquivo</strong> e certifique-se de que a importação do <code>ui.js</code> esteja correta e única, desta forma:
<response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-342 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-342 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3c8227074b9dd8a1&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_04ab7d3444922772&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-342 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-342">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-342 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-342 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3c8227074b9dd8a1&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_04ab7d3444922772&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-342"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-342"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-342"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-342" data-sourcepos="16:5-27:36"><span class="hljs-comment">// No topo do arquivo gameLogic.js</span>

<span class="hljs-comment">// Garanta que esta seja a única linha importando de './ui.js'</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> { showNarrativeScreen, showEndScreen } <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <span class="hljs-string">'./ui.js'</span>;

<span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> { gameState } <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <span class="hljs-string">'./gameState.js'</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> { phaseConfigs, images, MAP_WIDTH, MAP_HEIGHT, PLAYABLE_AREA_BORDER, VIEWPORT_WIDTH, VIEWPORT_HEIGHT } <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <span class="hljs-string">'./config.js'</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> { Enemy, DynamicEnemy, FinalBoss, Item, Portal } <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <span class="hljs-string">'./entities.js'</span>;

<span class="hljs-comment">// ... o resto do seu código ...</span>
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>
</li>
</ol><p data-sourcepos="29:1-29:229">Ao remover a importação antiga do final do arquivo e garantir que a nova importação no topo esteja correta, este erro de "identificador já declarado" será resolvido de uma vez por todas. Lamento muito por essa série de problemas.</p></div></message-content><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-footer gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c3831108472="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c3831108472="" _nghost-ng-c1702140789="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c3572881400="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3358885363-336"><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c1790889713="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-343 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-343"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-343 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" _nghost-ng-c1126443278="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-343 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1126443278="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Boa resposta" aria-label="Boa resposta" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger icon-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-pressed="false" aria-controls="feedback-f