thoughts-header-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c1786796508-348 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c1786796508-348"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-348">Mostrar raciocínio</span></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c1786796508-348"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c1786796508-348 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button></div><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----><!----><!----><!----><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="model-response-text ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3841436833="" id="message-content-id-r_25fb2254addf5d99" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3841436833="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_25fb2254addf5d99" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:137">Olá! Você está certo em apontar esses problemas. São dois bugs distintos que surgiram com as últimas alterações. Vamos corrigir os dois.</p><h3 data-sourcepos="3:1-3:32">1. A História Fora de Ordem</h3><p data-sourcepos="5:1-5:122">Este é um clássico erro de programação chamado "off-by-one" (erro por um). A lógica estava pegando o texto da fase errada.</p><p data-sourcepos="7:1-7:219"><strong>A Causa:</strong> O objeto que guardava as histórias usava chaves <code>1, 2, 3</code>, mas o código tentava acessá-lo como um array que começa em <code>0</code>. Isso fazia com que a primeira história fosse pulada e as outras ficassem atrasadas.</p><p data-sourcepos="9:1-9:85"><strong>A Solução:</strong> Vamos ajustar a estrutura dos textos e a forma como eles são chamados.</p><p data-sourcepos="11:1-11:49"><strong>No arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/js/gameLogic.js</code>:</strong></p><ol data-sourcepos="13:1-44:0">
<li data-sourcepos="13:1-34:7"><strong>Substitua</strong> o seu objeto <code>narrativeTexts</code> por este <strong>array</strong>:
<response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-353 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-353 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_25fb2254addf5d99&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_f2cdbb19d5084403&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-353 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-353">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-353 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-353 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_25fb2254addf5d99&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_f2cdbb19d5084403&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-353"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-353"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-353"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-353" data-sourcepos="14:5-34:6"><span class="hljs-comment">// Substitua o objeto 'narrativeTexts' por este array</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> narrativeTexts = [
  { <span class="hljs-comment">// Posição 0: Texto para iniciar a Fase 2</span>
    <span class="hljs-attr">title</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"Um Eco nas Profundezas"</span>,
    <span class="hljs-attr">subtitle</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"Você sobreviveu à primeira horda. Um calor estranho emana das paredes de rocha e um eco distante ressoa pela masmorra."</span>
  },
  { <span class="hljs-comment">// Posição 1: Texto para iniciar a Fase 3</span>
    <span class="hljs-attr">title</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"O Ar se Torna Rarefeito"</span>,
    <span class="hljs-attr">subtitle</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"Inimigos mais fortes surgem das sombras. O ar fica denso e a escuridão parece querer te engolir. O tesouro deve estar perto."</span>
  },
  { <span class="hljs-comment">// Posição 2: Texto para iniciar a Fase 4</span>
    <span class="hljs-attr">title</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"O Coração do Vulcão"</span>,
    <span class="hljs-attr">subtitle</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"O chão treme sob seus pés! Cinzas caem do teto e rios de lava brilham ao longe. A masmorra é o interior de um vulcão adormecido!"</span>
  },
  { <span class="hljs-comment">// Posição 3: Texto para iniciar a Fase 5 (Chefe)</span>
    <span class="hljs-attr">title</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"O Guardião Ancestral"</span>,
    <span class="hljs-attr">subtitle</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"Você chegou à câmara final. O tesouro está à vista, mas uma criatura colossal, forjada em fogo e rocha, desperta para protegê-lo."</span>
  }
];
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>
</li>
<li data-sourcepos="35:1-44:0">Dentro da função <code>checkPhaseCompletion</code>, <strong>altere a linha</strong> que busca a história:
<ul data-sourcepos="36:7-44:0">
