44699999690055847,-15 0.8899999856948853,-14.979999542236328 1.3270000219345093,-14.942000389099121"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_4913)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_4909)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_4902)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div><!----><!----></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c3358885363-360 has-thoughts"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-content ng-tns-c3358885363-360"><!----><model-thoughts _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-361 ng-star-inserted" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="model-thoughts ng-tns-c1786796508-361"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header ng-tns-c1786796508-361"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" mat-button="" data-test-id="thoughts-header-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c1786796508-361 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c1786796508-361"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-361">Mostrar raciocínio</span></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c1786796508-361"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c1786796508-361 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button></div><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----><!----><!----><!----><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="model-response-text has-thoughts ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c3841436833="" id="message-content-id-r_3bea915881a65cc8" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3841436833="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_3bea915881a65cc8" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:156">Com certeza! Adicionar perigos ambientais como poças de lava é uma ótima maneira de tornar uma fase mais interessante e desafiadora de uma forma diferente.</p><p data-sourcepos="3:1-3:175">Vamos dividir isso em etapas: primeiro, vamos diminuir um pouco a dificuldade dos inimigos na fase do vulcão e, em seguida, adicionaremos as poças de lava como um novo perigo.</p><h3 data-sourcepos="5:1-5:53">Passo 1: Diminuir a Dificuldade da Fase do Vulcão</h3><p data-sourcepos="7:1-7:106">Para equilibrar a nova dificuldade das poças de lava, vamos ajustar os parâmetros dos inimigos nesta fase.</p><p data-sourcepos="9:1-9:46"><strong>No arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/js/config.js</code>:</strong></p><ol data-sourcepos="11:1-29:0">
<li data-sourcepos="11:1-12:0">
<p data-sourcepos="11:5-11:131">Encontre a quarta configuração de fase no array <code>phaseConfigs</code> (lembre-se que a contagem começa em 0, então é a de índice <code>3</code>).</p>
</li>
<li data-sourcepos="13:1-29:0">
<p data-sourcepos="13:5-13:145"><strong>Substitua</strong> a configuração existente por esta, que tem uma duração menor, menos inimigos na tela e um intervalo maior entre os nascimentos:</p>
<response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-372 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-372 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-372 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-372">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-372 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-372 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-372"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-372"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-372"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-372" data-sourcepos="15:5-28:6"><span class="hljs-comment">// Configuração original da fase 4 (índice 3)</span>
<span class="hljs-comment">// { objectiveType: "survive", duration: 60, objectiveText: "Sobreviva por 60 segundos!", maxEnemies: 12, spawnInterval: 1500, enemyTypes: ["fast", "tank"], },</span>

<span class="hljs-comment">// Substitua pela configuração abaixo</span>
{ 
  <span class="hljs-attr">objectiveType</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"survive"</span>, 
  <span class="hljs-attr">duration</span>: <span class="hljs-number">50</span>, <span class="hljs-comment">// Duração diminuída de 60 para 50 segundos</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">objectiveText</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"Sobreviva ao calor infernal!"</span>, 
  <span class="hljs-attr">maxEnemies</span>: <span class="hljs-number">10</span>, <span class="hljs-comment">// Máximo de inimigos diminuído de 12 para 10</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">spawnInterval</span>: <span class="hljs-number">2000</span>, <span class="hljs-comment">// Intervalo entre inimigos aumentado de 1500ms para 2000ms</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">enemyTypes</span>: [<span class="hljs-string">"fast"</span>, <span class="hljs-string">"tank"</span>], 
},
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>
</li>
</ol><h3 data-sourcepos="30:1-30:39">Passo 2: Adicionar as Poças de Lava</h3><p data-sourcepos="32:1-32:50">Agora, vamos criar a lógica para as poças de lava.</p><h4 data-sourcepos="34:1-34:51">A. Atualizar o Estado do Jogo (<code>gameState.js</code>)</h4><p data-sourcepos="36:1-36:59">Precisamos de um lugar para armazenar nossas poças de lava.</p><p data-sourcepos="38:1-38:49"><strong>No arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/js/gameState.js</code>:</strong></p><ol data-sourcepos="40:1-42:0">
<li data-sourcepos="40:1-40:51">Adicione <code>lavaPools: []</code> ao objeto <code>gameState</code>.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="41:1-42:0">Adicione <code>lavaPools: []</code> à função <code>resetGameState</code> para limpar as poças ao reiniciar.</li>
</ol><p data-sourcepos="43:1-43:20">&lt;!-- end list --&gt;</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-373 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-373 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-373 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-373">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-373 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-373 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-373"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-373"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-373"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-373" data-sourcepos="45:1-63:1"><span class="hljs-comment">// Em gameState.js</span>

<span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> gameState = {
  <span class="hljs-comment">// ... outras propriedades</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">isPlayerInvincible</span>: <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>,
  <span class="hljs-attr">lavaPools</span>: [], <span class="hljs-comment">// &lt;&lt;&lt; ADICIONE ESTA LINHA</span>
};

<span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> { gameState };

<span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">resetGameState</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>) </span>{
  <span class="hljs-built_in">Object</span>.assign(gameState, {
    <span class="hljs-comment">// ... outras propriedades</span>
    <span class="hljs-attr">isPlayerInvincible</span>: <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>,
    <span class="hljs-attr">lavaPools</span>: [], <span class="hljs-comment">// &lt;&lt;&lt; E ADICIONE ESTA LINHA</span>
  });
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><h4 data-sourcepos="65:1-65:49">B. Criar a Classe <code>LavaPool</code> (<code>entities.js</code>)</h4><p data-sourcepos="67:1-67:61">Precisamos de uma "entidade" para representar a poça de lava.</p><p data-sourcepos="69:1-69:95"><strong>No arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/js/entities.js</code>, adicione esta nova classe no final do arquivo:</strong></p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-374 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-374 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-374 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-374">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-374 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-374 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-374"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-374"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-374"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-374" data-sourcepos="71:1-96:1"><span class="hljs-comment">// Adicione esta classe no final de entities.js</span>

<span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">LavaPool</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">extends</span> <span class="hljs-title">Character</span> </span>{
    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">constructor</span>(<span class="hljs-params">x, y, radius</span>)</span> {
        <span class="hljs-comment">// A hitbox será um quadrado baseado no raio</span>
        <span class="hljs-built_in">super</span>(x - radius, y - radius, radius * <span class="hljs-number">2</span>, radius * <span class="hljs-number">2</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>);
        <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.radius = radius;
        <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.damage = <span class="hljs-number">10</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// Dano que a lava causa por pulso</span>
        <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.animationTimer = <span class="hljs-built_in">Math</span>.random() * <span class="hljs-number">1000</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// Para animação assíncrona</span>
    }

    <span class="hljs-comment">// Função para desenhar a lava (um círculo vermelho pulsante)</span>
    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">draw</span>(<span class="hljs-params">ctx</span>)</span> {
        <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.animationTimer += <span class="hljs-number">16</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// Aproximadamente 60fps</span>
        <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> pulse = <span class="hljs-built_in">Math</span>.sin(<span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.animationTimer / <span class="hljs-number">300</span>) * <span class="hljs-number">0.2</span> + <span class="hljs-number">0.8</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// Pulsa entre 80% e 100%</span>

        ctx.globalAlpha = <span class="hljs-number">0.5</span> * pulse; <span class="hljs-comment">// Define a transparência com o pulso</span>
        ctx.fillStyle = <span class="hljs-string">"#ff4500"</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// Cor de lava (laranja-vermelho)</span>
        ctx.beginPath();
        ctx.arc(<span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.x + <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.radius, <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.y + <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.radius, <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.radius * pulse, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-built_in">Math</span>.PI * <span class="hljs-number">2</span>);
        ctx.fill();
        ctx.globalAlpha = <span class="hljs-number">1.0</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// Restaura a transparência global</span>
    }
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><h4 data-sourcepos="98:1-98:52">C. Posicionar as Poças de Lava (<code>gameLogic.js</code>)</h4><p data-sourcepos="100:1-100:61">Vamos criar as poças de lava quando a fase do vulcão começar.</p><p data-sourcepos="102:1-102:49"><strong>No arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/js/gameLogic.js</code>:</strong></p><ol data-sourcepos="104:1-161:0">
<li data-sourcepos="104:1-109:0">
<p data-sourcepos="104:5-104:56">Importe a nova classe <code>LavaPool</code> no topo do arquivo:</p>
<response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-375 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-375 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-375 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-375">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-375 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-375 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-375"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-375"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-375"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-375" data-sourcepos="106:5-108:91"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> { Enemy, DynamicEnemy, FinalBoss, Item, Portal, LavaPool } <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <span class="hljs-string">'./entities.js'</span>;
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>
</li>
<li data-sourcepos="110:1-161:0">
<p data-sourcepos="110:5-110:102"><strong>Substitua</strong> sua função <code>setupPhase</code> por esta versão, que adiciona a lógica de criação das poças:</p>
<response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-376 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-376 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-376 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-376">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-376 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-376 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-376"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-376"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-376"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-376" data-sourcepos="112:5-158:5"><span class="hljs-comment">// Substitua a função setupPhase inteira</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">setupPhase</span>(<span class="hljs-params">phaseIndex</span>) </span>{
    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!phaseConfigs[phaseIndex]) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;

    <span class="hljs-comment">// Limpa o estado da fase anterior</span>
    <span class="hljs-built_in">Object</span>.assign(gameState, {
        <span class="hljs-attr">phase</span>: phaseIndex,
        <span class="hljs-attr">enemies</span>: [],
        <span class="hljs-attr">items</span>: [],
        <span class="hljs-attr">projectiles</span>: [],
        <span class="hljs-attr">enemyProjectiles</span>: [],
        <span class="hljs-attr">portal</span>: <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>,
        <span class="hljs-attr">lavaPools</span>: [], <span class="hljs-comment">// Limpa as poças de lava</span>
        <span class="hljs-attr">phaseStartTime</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">Date</span>.now(),
        <span class="hljs-attr">lastEnemySpawnTime</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0</span>,
    });

    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> config = phaseConfigs[phaseIndex];
    <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="hljs-string">"objective-text"</span>).textContent = <span class="hljs-string">`Objetivo: <span class="hljs-subst">${config.objectiveText}</span>`</span>;

    <span class="hljs-comment">// Lógica para o chefe</span>
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> bossHealthContainer = <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="hljs-string">"boss-health-container"</span>);
    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (config.objectiveType === <span class="hljs-string">"defeat_boss"</span>) {
        bossHealthContainer.classList.remove(<span class="hljs-string">"hidden"</span>);
        spawnEnemy(<span class="hljs-string">'final_boss'</span>);
    } <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> {
        bossHealthContainer.classList.add(<span class="hljs-string">"hidden"</span>);
    }

    <span class="hljs-comment">// &lt;&lt;&lt; LÓGICA PARA CRIAR AS POÇAS DE LAVA &gt;&gt;&gt;</span>
    <span class="hljs-comment">// Apenas na fase 4 (índice 3)</span>
    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (phaseIndex === <span class="hljs-number">3</span>) {
        <span class="hljs-comment">// **IMPORTANTE**: Ajuste as coordenadas (x, y) e o raio para corresponder ao seu cenário!</span>
        <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> poolLocations = [
            { <span class="hljs-attr">x</span>: <span class="hljs-number">200</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">y</span>: <span class="hljs-number">300</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">50</span> },
            { <span class="hljs-attr">x</span>: <span class="hljs-number">800</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">y</span>: <span class="hljs-number">250</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">70</span> },
            { <span class="hljs-attr">x</span>: <span class="hljs-number">400</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">y</span>: <span class="hljs-number">700</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">60</span> },
            { <span class="hljs-attr">x</span>: <span class="hljs-number">750</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">y</span>: <span class="hljs-number">800</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">40</span> },
        ];

        poolLocations.forEach(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">p</span> =&gt;</span> {
            gameState.lavaPools.push(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> LavaPool(p.x, p.y, p.radius));
        });
    }
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>
<p data-sourcepos="160:5-160:220"><strong>Observação:</strong> Eu coloquei coordenadas de exemplo. Você deve ajustar os valores de <code>x</code>, <code>y</code> e <code>radius</code> no array <code>poolLocations</code> para que as poças de lava fiquem em cima das áreas de lava do seu cenário <code>vulcan.png</code>.</p>
</li>
</ol><h4 data-sourcepos="162:1-162:43">D. Aplicar Dano e Desenhar (<code>main.js</code>)</h4><p data-sourcepos="164:1-164:76">Finalmente, vamos fazer as poças de lava causarem dano e aparecerem no jogo.</p><p data-sourcepos="166:1-166:44"><strong>No arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/js/main.js</code>:</strong></p><ol data-sourcepos="168:1-217:0">
<li data-sourcepos="168:1-172:7">Adicione uma variável para controlar o tempo do dano da lava. Coloque-a perto do topo do arquivo, fora de qualquer função:
<response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-377 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-377 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-377 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-377">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-377 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-377 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-377"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-377"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-377"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-377" data-sourcepos="169:5-172:31"><span class="hljs-comment">// Adicione esta linha perto do topo do arquivo</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> lastLavaDamageTime = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>
</li>
<li data-sourcepos="173:1-198:7">Modifique a função <code>update</code> para incluir a verificação de colisão com a lava:
<response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-378 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-378 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-378 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-378">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-378 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-378 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-378"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-378"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-378"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-378" data-sourcepos="174:5-198:5"><span class="hljs-comment">// Adicione este trecho dentro da função update(), logo após o loop dos itens.</span>

  <span class="hljs-comment">// ... (loop dos items) ...</span>
  <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> i = gameState.items.length - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &gt;= <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i--) {
    <span class="hljs-comment">// ...</span>
  }

  <span class="hljs-comment">// &lt;&lt;&lt; LÓGICA DE DANO DA LAVA &gt;&gt;&gt;</span>
  <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> pool <span class="hljs-keyword">of</span> gameState.lavaPools) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (isColliding(gameState.player, pool)) {
          <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> now = <span class="hljs-built_in">Date</span>.now();
          <span class="hljs-comment">// Causa dano a cada 700ms se o jogador estiver na lava</span>
          <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (now - lastLavaDamageTime &gt; <span class="hljs-number">700</span>) {
              gameState.player.takeDamage(pool.damage);
              lastLavaDamageTime = now;
          }
          <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// Sai do loop se já encontrou uma colisão</span>
      }
  }

  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (gameState.portal) gameState.portal.update();
  checkPhaseCompletion();
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>
</li>
<li data-sourcepos="199:1-217:0">Modifique a função <code>draw</code> para desenhar as poças de lava:
<response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-379 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-379 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-379 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-379">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-379 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-379 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_3bea915881a65cc8&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_053581065e9ed824&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-379"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-379"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-379"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-379" data-sourcepos="200:5-216:5"><span class="hljs-comment">// Adicione este trecho dentro da função draw(), antes de desenhar o jogador</span>
<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">draw</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>) </span>{
  <span class="hljs-comment">// ...</span>
  ctx.translate(-gameState.camera.x, -gameState.camera.y);
  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (bgImage &amp;&amp; bgImage.complete &amp;&amp; bgImage.naturalWidth !== <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) {
    ctx.drawImage(bgImage, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, MAP_WIDTH, MAP_HEIGHT);
  }

  <span class="hljs-comment">// &lt;&lt;&lt; DESENHA AS POÇAS DE LAVA &gt;&gt;&gt;</span>
  gameState.lavaPools.forEach(<span class="hljs-function">(<span class="hljs-params">pool</span>) =&gt;</span> pool &amp;&amp; pool.draw(ctx));

  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (gameState.portal) gameState.portal.draw(ctx);
  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (gameState.player) gameState.player.draw(ctx);
  <span class="hljs-comment">// ...</span>
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>
</li>
</ol><p data-sourcepos="218:1-218:239">Pronto! Com todas essas alterações, sua fase do vulcão será um pouco mais fácil em termos de inimigos, mas terá o novo desafio das poças de lava que causam dano ao jogador. Lembre-se de ajustar a posição delas para combinar com seu mapa!</p></div></message-content><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-footer has-thoughts gap complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c3831108472="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c3831108472="" _nghost-ng-c1702140789="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c3572881400="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3358885363-360"><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c1790889713="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-380 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-380"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-380 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" _nghost-ng-c1126443278="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-380 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1126443278="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Boa resposta" aria-label="Boa resposta" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger icon-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-pressed="false" aria-controls="