dd543d65" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:216">Olá. Este novo erro, <code>ReferenceError: e is not defined</code>, é diferente dos anteriores. Ele significa que o código está tentando usar uma variável chamada <code>e</code> que não foi declarada ou não existe nesse trecho específico.</p><p data-sourcepos="3:1-3:58">Isso geralmente acontece por um pequeno erro de digitação.</p><h3 data-sourcepos="5:1-5:14">O Problema</h3><p data-sourcepos="7:1-7:128">O erro está no arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/js/gameLogic.js</code>, dentro da função <code>setupPhase</code>, na parte que adiciona as poças de lava.</p><p data-sourcepos="9:1-9:172">Quando iteramos sobre as localizações das poças, definimos uma variável <code>p</code> para cada uma, mas provavelmente você usou a letra <code>e</code> por engano na hora de criar a <code>LavaPool</code>.</p><p data-sourcepos="11:1-11:49"><strong>O código com o erro provavelmente está assim:</strong></p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-407 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-407 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_62b89450dd543d65&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_118604708232eb94&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-407 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-407">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-407 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-407 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_62b89450dd543d65&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_118604708232eb94&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-407"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-407"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-407"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-407" data-sourcepos="13:1-18:3">poolLocations.forEach(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">p</span> =&gt;</span> {
    <span class="hljs-comment">// O erro está aqui: usando 'e' em vez de 'p'</span>
    gameState.lavaPools.push(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> LavaPool(e.x, e.y, e.radius)); 
});
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><h3 data-sourcepos="20:1-20:14">A Correção</h3><p data-sourcepos="22:1-22:83">Você precisa garantir que está usando a variável <code>p</code> que foi definida no <code>forEach</code>.</p><ol data-sourcepos="24:1-28:0">
<li data-sourcepos="24:1-24:57"><strong>Abra o arquivo:</strong> <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/js/gameLogic.js</code></li>
<li data-sourcepos="25:1-25:39"><strong>Encontre a função:</strong> <code>setupPhase</code></li>
<li data-sourcepos="26:1-26:74">Localize o bloco <code>if (phaseIndex === 3)</code> que cuida da criação da lava.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="27:1-28:0"><strong>Corrija o loop</strong>, substituindo <code>e</code> por <code>p</code>. O bloco correto deve ser este:</li>
</ol><p data-sourcepos="29:1-29:20">&lt;!-- end list --&gt;</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-408 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-408 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_62b89450dd543d65&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_118604708232eb94&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-408 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-408">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-408 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-408 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_62b89450dd543d65&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_118604708232eb94&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-408"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-408"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-408"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-408" data-sourcepos="31:1-48:1"><span class="hljs-comment">// Dentro da função setupPhase, em gameLogic.js</span>

<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (phaseIndex === <span class="hljs-number">3</span>) {
    <span class="hljs-comment">// **IMPORTANTE**: Ajuste as coordenadas (x, y) e o raio para corresponder ao seu cenário!</span>
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> poolLocations = [
        { <span class="hljs-attr">x</span>: <span class="hljs-number">200</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">y</span>: <span class="hljs-number">300</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">50</span> },
        { <span class="hljs-attr">x</span>: <span class="hljs-number">800</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">y</span>: <span class="hljs-number">250</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">70</span> },
        { <span class="hljs-attr">x</span>: <span class="hljs-number">400</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">y</span>: <span class="hljs-number">700</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">60</span> },
        { <span class="hljs-attr">x</span>: <span class="hljs-number">750</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">y</span>: <span class="hljs-number">800</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">40</span> },
    ];

    <span class="hljs-comment">// Garanta que 'p' seja usado aqui dentro</span>
    poolLocations.forEach(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">p</span> =&gt;</span> {
        gameState.lavaPools.push(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> LavaPool(p.x, p.y, p.radius));
    });
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><p data-sourcepos="50:1-50:124">Ao fazer essa simples troca de <code>e</code> por <code>p</code>, o erro de referência desaparecerá e as poças de lava serão criadas corretamente.</p></div></message-content><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-footer gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c3831108472="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c3831108472="" _nghost-ng-c1702140789="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c3572881400="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3358885363-402"><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c1790889713="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-409 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-409"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-409 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" _nghost-ng-c1126443278="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-409 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1126443278="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Boa resposta" aria-label="Boa resposta" class="m