der-button-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c1786796508-441"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-441">Mostrar raciocínio</span></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c1786796508-441"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c1786796508-441 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button></div><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----><!----><!----><!----><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="model-response-text ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3841436833="" id="message-content-id-r_bfca76e74a6f908e" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3841436833="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_bfca76e74a6f908e" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:182">Entendido. O arquivo <code>vulcan.jpg</code> que você enviou é um padrão repetitivo, como uma textura. Você quer um cenário, uma paisagem de um vulcão, mas sem as poças de lava na área jogável.</p><p data-sourcepos="3:1-3:182">Compreendi perfeitamente. Minha última tentativa foi de um cenário de caverna, mas vamos tentar uma abordagem diferente para ter certeza de que chegamos a um resultado que te agrada.</p><p data-sourcepos="5:1-5:24">Que tal esta nova ideia?</p><p data-sourcepos="7:1-7:399"><strong>Uma cena em pixel art vista de um ângulo mais alto. O jogador estaria em uma ponte larga de rocha negra e rachada que atravessa um abismo. Abaixo da ponte, um mar de lava agitado ilumina a cena por baixo com um brilho laranja intenso. Ao fundo, as paredes da caverna vulcânica se perdem em uma névoa quente e avermelhada. A ponte em si (a área de jogo) seria de rocha escura e segura, sem poças.</strong></p><p data-sourcepos="9:1-10:77">Vou gerar essa nova imagem para você.
Aqui está a nova imagem, com a perspectiva de uma ponte sobre um mar de lava.</p><p data-sourcepos="12:1-12:55"><div class="attachment-container generated-images"><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><generated-image _nghost-ng-c939924418="" class="ng-star-inserted" style="aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c939924418="" class="loader animate"></div><single-image _ngcontent-ng-c939924418="" class="generated-image large" _nghost-ng-c133898763="" data-image-attachment-index="0" jslog="185864;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_bfca76e74a6f908e&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_4eb725b7002536f6&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><div _ngcontent-ng-c133898763="" replace-fife-images-at-export="" class="image-container replace-fife-images-at-export ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c133898763="" class="overlay-container ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c133898763="" class="image-button ng-star-inserted" jslog="181501;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_bfca76e74a6f908e&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_4eb725b7002536f6&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><img _ngcontent-ng-c133898763="" class="image loaded" alt="Imagem de " src="./hud-background_files/unnamed(3).png"></button><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c939924418="" overlay="" hide-from-message-actions="" class="generated-image-controls hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted"><download-generated-image-button _ngcontent-ng-c939924418="" _nghost-ng-c3892761706=""><button _ngcontent-ng-c3892761706="" mat-button="" aria-label="Baixar imagem no tamanho original" mattooltip="Baixar no tamanho original" data-test-id="download-generated-image-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger generated-image-button on-hover-button mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" jslog="185865;track:generic_click;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_bfca76e74a6f908e&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_4eb725b7002536f6&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true" aria-describedby="cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-255" cdk-describedby-host="ng-1"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3892761706="" class="button-icon-wrapper"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3892761706="" role="img" fonticon="download" class="mat-icon notranslate button-icon google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="download"></mat-icon><!----></div></span><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----></download-generated-image-button></div><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></single-image></generated-image><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element></div></p><p data-sourcepos="14:1-14:130"><strong>Lembrete:</strong> Caso a imagem não apareça diretamente para você (e apareça apenas o link), por favor, siga os passos que discutimos:</p><ol data-sourcepos="15:1-17:0">
<li data-sourcepos="15:1-15:27"><strong>Copie</strong> o link acima.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="16:1-17:0"><strong>Cole</strong> em uma nova aba do seu navegador e pressione Enter para ver e salvar a imagem.</li>
</ol><p data-sourcepos="18:1-18:121">Depois de salvar, renomeie para <code>vulcan.png</code> e coloque na sua pasta <code>images</code> para que o jogo a utilize na fase do vulcão.</p></div></message-content><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-footer gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c3831108472="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c3831108472="" _nghost-ng-c1702140789="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c3572881400="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3358885363-438"><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c1790889713="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-442 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-442"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c1790889713-442 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c1790889713="" _nghost-ng-c1126443278="" class="ng-tns-c1790889713-442 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1126443278="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Boa resposta" aria-label="Boa resposta" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger icon-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-pressed="false" aria-controls="feedback-form-32" jslog="173913;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_bfca7