icons ng-tns-c1786796508-461"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c1786796508-461 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button></div><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----><!----><!----><!----><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="model-response-text ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3841436833="" id="message-content-id-r_76cc3cf69f3d4d80" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3841436833="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_76cc3cf69f3d4d80" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:160">Claro! Vamos fazer uma repaginação completa no HUD e nos botões para que eles se encaixem melhor na estética "pixel art" e na temática de masmorra do seu jogo.</p><p data-sourcepos="3:1-3:116">A ideia é criar uma interface mais limpa, temática e com botões que pareçam "clicáveis" e parte do universo do jogo.</p><h3 data-sourcepos="5:1-5:49">Passo 1: Remover a Pontuação e Ajustar o HTML</h3><p data-sourcepos="7:1-7:120">Primeiro, vamos remover o contador de pontos que não está sendo usado e preparar os botões para receberem o novo estilo.</p><p data-sourcepos="9:1-9:40"><strong>No arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/index.html</code>:</strong></p><ol data-sourcepos="11:1-13:0">
<li data-sourcepos="11:1-11:80"><strong>Remova a linha da pontuação</strong> de dentro da <code>div</code> com a classe <code>hud-stats</code>.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="12:1-13:0"><strong>Adicione a classe <code>pixel-button</code></strong> a todos os botões do jogo. Vamos criar essa classe no CSS logo em seguida.</li>
</ol><p data-sourcepos="14:1-14:57"><strong>Substitua o conteúdo da sua tag <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> por este:</strong></p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-465 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-465 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_76cc3cf69f3d4d80&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_84c897a79e822cae&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-465 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-465">HTML</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-465 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-465 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_76cc3cf69f3d4d80&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_84c897a79e822cae&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><spa