atrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_6201)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="2" d=" M0,-15 C4.894000053405762,-15 9.244000434875488,-12.651000022888184 11.982999801635742,-9.020000457763672"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,16,16)" opacity="1"><g opacity="1" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_6197)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="2" d=" M-4.383999824523926,-14.347999572753906 C-2.996999979019165,-14.772000312805176 -1.524999976158142,-15 0,-15 C0,-15 0,-15 0,-15 C1.7100000381469727,-15 3.3540000915527344,-14.713000297546387 4.886000156402588,-14.1850004196167"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_6193)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_6189)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_6182)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div><!----><!----></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c3358885363-471 has-thoughts"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-content ng-tns-c3358885363-471"><!----><model-thoughts _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-473 ng-star-inserted" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="model-thoughts ng-tns-c1786796508-473"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header ng-tns-c1786796508-473"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" mat-button="" data-test-id="thoughts-header-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c1786796508-473 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c1786796508-473"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-473">Mostrar raciocínio</span></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c1786796508-473"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c1786796508-473 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button></div><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----><!----><!----><!----><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="model-response-text ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3841436833="" id="message-content-id-r_4f650b6c7d354a14" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3841436833="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_4f650b6c7d354a14" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:194">Compreendo. O erro <code>404 (Not Found)</code> é muito comum e significa exatamente o que diz: o navegador tentou buscar o arquivo <code>menu-background.png</code> no local que o CSS indicou, mas não o encontrou lá.</p><p data-sourcepos="3:1-3:50">Isso quase sempre acontece por uma de duas razões:</p><ol data-sourcepos="5:1-7:0">
<li data-sourcepos="5:1-5:84">O arquivo não está na pasta <code>images</code> ou está com um nome ligeiramente diferente.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="6:1-7:0">O caminho (<code>path</code>) no arquivo CSS para a imagem está um pouco diferente do que o servidor local espera.</li>
</ol><p data-sourcepos="8:1-8:79">Vamos focar na solução mais provável e robusta, que é ajustar o caminho no CSS.</p><h3 data-sourcepos="10:1-10:14">A Correção</h3><p data-sourcepos="12:1-12:192">Usaremos um caminho "absoluto" a partir da raiz do seu projeto. Isso diz ao navegador para procurar a pasta <code>images</code> diretamente na pasta principal do seu jogo, o que é menos propenso a erros.</p><p data-sourcepos="14:1-14:54"><strong>1. Abra o arquivo:</strong> <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/css/main.css</code>.</p><p data-sourcepos="16:1-16:53"><strong>2. Encontre a regra de estilo para <code>#start-menu</code></strong>.</p><p data-sourcepos="18:1-18:41"><strong>3. Altere a linha <code>background-image</code>:</strong></p><ul data-sourcepos="20:3-31:0">
<li data-sourcepos="20:3-25:0">
<p data-sourcepos="20:5-20:45"><strong>Sua linha atual provavelmente é esta:</strong></p>
<response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-477 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-477 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_4f650b6c7d354a14&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_d6add4104539f0eb&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-477 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-477">CSS</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-477 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-477 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_4f650b6c7d354a14&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_d6add4104539f0eb&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-477"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-477"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-477"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-477" data-sourcepos="22:5-24:119"><span class="hljs-attribute">background-image</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">linear-gradient</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.6</span>), <span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.6</span>)), <span class="hljs-built_in">url</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'../../images/menu-background.png'</span>);
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>
</li>
<li data-sourcepos="26:3-31:0">
<p data-sourcepos="26:5-26:48"><strong>Altere-a para esta (removendo os <code>../</code>):</strong></p>
<response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-478 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-478 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_4f650b6c7d354a14&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_d6add4104539f0eb&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-478 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-478">CSS</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-478 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-478 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_4f650b6c7d354a14&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_d6add4104539f0eb&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-478"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-478"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-478"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-478" data-sourcepos="28:5-30:114"><span class="hljs-attribute">background-image</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">linear-gradient</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.6</span>), <span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.6</span>)), <span class="hljs-built_in">url</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'/images/menu-background.png'</span>);
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>
</li>
</ul><p data-sourcepos="32:1-32:56"><strong>Como a regra completa para <code>#start-menu</code> deve ficar:</strong></p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-479 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-479 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_4f650b6c7d354a14&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_d6add4104539f0eb&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-479 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-479">CSS</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-479 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-479 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_4f650b6c7d354a14&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_d6add4104539f0eb&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-479"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-479"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-479"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-479" data-sourcepos="34:1-59:1"><span class="hljs-comment">/* Em main.css */</span>

<span class="hljs-selector-id">#start-menu</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: absolute;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">top</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">left</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">width</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100%</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">height</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100%</span>;
  
  <span class="hljs-comment">/* A linha abaixo foi corrigida para usar um caminho absoluto */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-image</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">linear-gradient</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.6</span>), <span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.6</span>)), <span class="hljs-built_in">url</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'/images/menu-background.png'</span>);
  
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-size</span>: cover;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-position</span>: center;

  <span class="hljs-attribute">display</span>: flex;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">flex-direction</span>: column;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">justify-content</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">align-items</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">text-align</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">font-family</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"Press Start 2P"</span>, cursive;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">z-index</span>: <span class="hljs-number">100</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">color</span>: <span class="hljs-number">#fff</span>;
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><p data-sourcepos="61:1-61:213">Ao colocar a barra <code>/</code> no início do caminho (<code>/images/...</code>), instruímos o navegador a procurar a pasta <code>images</code> a partir do diretório raiz do seu projeto (onde o <code>index.html</code> está), o que deve resolver o erro 404.</p><p data-sourcepos="63:1-63:57"><strong>Se o erro persistir, por favor, confirme duas coisas:</strong></p><ul data-sourcepos="65:3-66:102">
<li data-sourcepos="65:3-65:53">A imagem está realmente dentro da pasta <code>images</code>?</li>
<li data-sourcepos="66:3-66:102">O nome do arquivo é exatamente <code>menu-background.png</code> (e não <code>.jpg</code> ou com alguma letra maiúscula)?</li>
