y="1"><g opacity="1" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_6713)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="2" d=" M-6.172999858856201,13.67300033569336 C-11.37600040435791,11.317999839782715 -15,6.078999996185303 -15,0 C-15,-3.8010001182556152 -13.583000183105469,-7.2729997634887695 -11.25,-9.918000221252441"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,16,16)" opacity="1"><g opacity="1" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_6709)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="2" d=" M-4.626999855041504,-14.272000312805176 C-3.1689999103546143,-14.744000434875488 -1.6139999628067017,-15 0,-15 C0,-15 0,-15 0,-15 C1.6239999532699585,-15 3.187999963760376,-14.741000175476074 4.6539998054504395,-14.262999534606934"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_6705)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_6701)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_6694)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div><!----><!----></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3358885363="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c3358885363-513 has-thoughts"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="response-content ng-tns-c3358885363-513"><!----><model-thoughts _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" _nghost-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-515 ng-star-inserted" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="model-thoughts ng-tns-c1786796508-515"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header ng-tns-c1786796508-515"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" mat-button="" data-test-id="thoughts-header-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c1786796508-515 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c1786796508-515"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="ng-tns-c1786796508-515">Mostrar raciocínio</span></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c1786796508-515"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1786796508="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c1786796508-515 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button></div><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----><!----><!----><!----><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c927349975="" class="model-response-text ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3841436833="" id="message-content-id-r_e80d0b17692b2a10" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3841436833="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_e80d0b17692b2a10" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:213">Entendido. Peço desculpas que o ajuste anterior não tenha ficado bom. Vamos fazer uma nova refinação, sendo mais agressivos na redução do tamanho e usando uma técnica diferente e mais precisa para a centralização.</p><p data-sourcepos="3:1-3:245">O problema da centralização provavelmente ocorre porque os elementos à esquerda (barra de vida) e à direita (botão de pausa) não têm o mesmo tamanho, então o <code>flex-box</code> não consegue centralizar o elemento do meio perfeitamente em relação à tela.</p><p data-sourcepos="5:1-5:45">Vamos resolver ambos os problemas de uma vez.</p><h3 data-sourcepos="7:1-7:14">A Solução:</h3><p data-sourcepos="9:1-9:79">As alterações serão feitas novamente no arquivo <code>ECOM00_jogo/src/css/main.css</code>.</p><p data-sourcepos="11:1-11:112"><strong>Substitua</strong> a seção de estilos do HUD que você tem atualmente por esta versão totalmente nova e mais compacta.</p><p data-sourcepos="13:1-13:54"><strong>Encontre e substitua este bloco em seu <code>main.css</code>:</strong></p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-519 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-519 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_e80d0b17692b2a10&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_685d797a50c73632&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-519 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-519">CSS</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-519 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-519 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_e80d0b17692b2a10&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_685d797a50c73632&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-519"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-519"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-519"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-519" data-sourcepos="15:1-20:1"><span class="hljs-comment">/* === HUD REFINADO E MENOR === */</span>
<span class="hljs-selector-id">#hud</span> {
    <span class="hljs-comment">/* ... seu código atual ... */</span>
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><p data-sourcepos="22:1-22:25"><strong>Por este novo código:</strong></p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-520 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1224449439-520 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_e80d0b17692b2a10&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_685d797a50c73632&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1224449439-520 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-520">CSS</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1224449439-520 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" aria-label="Copiar o código" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copiar o código" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1224449439-520 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_e80d0b17692b2a10&quot;,&quot;c_a99c9efdec04d64a&quot;,null,&quot;rc_685d797a50c73632&quot;,null,null,&quot;pt&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1224449439-520"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1224449439-520"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" class="ng-tns-c1224449439-520"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1224449439="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1224449439-520" data-sourcepos="24:1-91:1"><span class="hljs-comment">/* === HUD FINAL - COMPACTO E CENTRALIZADO === */</span>
<span class="hljs-selector-id">#hud</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">padding</span>: <span class="hljs-number">5px</span> <span class="hljs-number">10px</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Padding geral ainda menor */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-color</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.5</span>);
  <span class="hljs-attribute">border-bottom</span>: <span class="hljs-number">2px</span> solid <span class="hljs-number">#333</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">color</span>: <span class="hljs-number">#fff</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">text-shadow</span>: <span class="hljs-number">1px</span> <span class="hljs-number">1px</span> <span class="hljs-number">1px</span> <span class="hljs-number">#000</span>;
}

<span class="hljs-selector-class">.hud-top</span> { 
  <span class="hljs-attribute">display</span>: flex; 
  <span class="hljs-attribute">justify-content</span>: space-between; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Mantém a vida na esquerda e o pause na direita */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">align-items</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: relative; <span class="hljs-comment">/* NECESSÁRIO para a centralização absoluta da fase */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">height</span>: <span class="hljs-number">20px</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Altura fixa para alinhar tudo */</span>
}

<span class="hljs-comment">/* Barra de Vida - Ainda menor */</span>
<span class="hljs-selector-id">#player-health-container</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: relative; 
  <span class="hljs-attribute">width</span>: <span class="hljs-number">130px</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Mais estreita */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">height</span>: <span class="hljs-number">18px</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Mais fina */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-color</span>: <span class="hljs-number">#333</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">border</span>: <span class="hljs-number">2px</span> solid <span class="hljs-number">#222</span>;
}
<span class="hljs-selector-id">#player-health-text</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="hljs-number">11px</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Fonte bem pequena */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">line-height</span>: <span class="hljs-number">16px</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Ajusta o alinhamento vertical */</span>
}
<span class="hljs-selector-id">#player-health-bar</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">border-radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Remove o radius para um look mais simples */</span>
}


<span class="hljs-comment">/* --- TÉCNICA DE CENTRALIZAÇÃO PRECISA DA FASE --- */</span>
<span class="hljs-selector-class">.hud-stats</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: absolute; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Retira do fluxo normal do flex */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">left</span>: <span class="hljs-number">50%</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Posiciona a 50% da largura da tela */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">top</span>: <span class="hljs-number">50%</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Posiciona a 50% da altura do HUD */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">transform</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">translate</span>(-<span class="hljs-number">50%</span>, -<span class="hljs-number">50%</span>); <span class="hljs-comment">/* Puxa o elemento de volta pela metade do seu tamanho */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="hljs-number">16px</span>;
}
<span class="hljs-selector-class">.hud-stats</span> <span class="hljs-selector-tag">p</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">margin</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
}

<span class="hljs-comment">/* Botão de Pausa - Menor */</span>
<span class="hljs-selector-id">#pause-button</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="hljs-number">10px</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">padding</span>: <span class="hljs-number">5px</span> <span class="hljs-number">10px</span>;
}

<span class="hljs-comment">/* Objetivo da Fase - Mais compacto */</span>
<span class="hljs-selector-class">.hud-bottom</span> {
  <span class="hljs-attribute">text-align</span>: center;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">margin-top</span>: <span class="hljs-number">5px</span>;
}
<span class="hljs-selector-id">#objective-text</span> { 
  <span class="hljs-attribute">display</span>: inline-block;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">padding</span>: <span class="hljs-number">2px</span> <span class="hljs-number">10px</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Padding vertical diminuído */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">background-color</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.4</span>);
  <span class="hljs-attribute">border-radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">10px</span>;
  <span class="hljs-attribute">color</span>: <span class="hljs-number">#ffc107</span>; 
  <span class="hljs-attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="hljs-number">14px</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Fonte menor */</span>
  <span class="hljs-attribute">border</span>: <span class="hljs-number">1px</span> solid <span class="hljs-built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="hljs-number">255</span>, <span class="hljs-number">255</span>, <span class="hljs-number">255</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.1</span>);
}
</code></pre><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><h3 data-sourcepos="93:1-93:35">O que Mudou e Por que Funciona:</h3><ol data-sourcepos="95:1-101:0">
<li data-sourcepos="95:1-95:154"><strong>Tamanho:</strong> Todos os valores de <code>padding</code>, <code>height</code>, <code>width</code> e <code>font-size</code> foram reduzidos ainda mais para criar um HUD bem mais discreto e compacto.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="96:1-101:0"><strong>Centralização da Fase:</strong>
<ul data-sourcepos="97:7-101:0">
<li data-sourcepos="97:7-97:80">A nova técnica usa <code>position: absolute</code> no texto da fase (<code>.hud-stats</code>).</li>
<li data-sourcepos="98:7-98:81">Nós o posicionamos exatamente a <code>50%</code> da esquerda e <code>50%</code> do topo do HUD.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="99:7-99:219">O <code>transform: translate(-50%, -50%)</code> então move o elemento de volta pela metade de sua própria largura e altura. O resultado é uma centralização matemática perfeita, independente do tamanho dos outros elementos.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="100:7-101:0">Para isso funcionar, o elemento pai (<code>.hud-top</code>) precisa ter <code>position: relative</code>.</li>
</ul>
</li>
